title: We Fought a Viking Horde...
author: JackManifoldTV
description:
I took TommyInnit and Ranboo to fight a group of REAL Vikings! This was really weird...

When I say real Vikings, I more mean like people who take pretending to be them VERY seriously, which is about as real you can get since apparently all the real ones died. The swords were very real though haha
